# CUIGG Reporting Tool (Report Maker) — environment configuration.
# Copy to .env (or export these vars) when deploying.

# --- Report Maker → hub back-link -------------------------------------------
# Where the sidebar "← WinnerFlags × CUIGG hub" link points. Set this to the
# deployed hub URL in production.
HUB_URL=http://localhost:3000

# --- Hub → Report Maker link (set on the HUB, shown here for reference) ------
# The WinnerFlags × CUIGG hub (the Next.js app) opens its "Report Maker" card
# at NEXT_PUBLIC_REPORT_MAKER_URL. Point that variable at THIS app's deployed
# URL so the hub links to the live Report Maker. For example:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_REPORT_MAKER_URL=https://reporting.councils.example
# Locally the Streamlit app serves on http://localhost:8501.
